^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, let's talk about this hand. The bidding in particular. 1S and 2C are fine as is pass by Dee. Now, lets talk about what Roberta should do. One of the things to consider when it goes bid-overcall-pass-pass is a reopening double. Especially if you are short in the overcalled suit. Remember, since we play negative doubles, Dee cannot make a penalty double. So, it is up to the opener to protect against a possible penalty double by partner by reopening with a double.|
