NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|However, with Roberta's massive two suiter, 2D is a much better bid than a reopening double. But you definitely need to keep reopening doubles in mind, and strain to make them when you are short of the overcalled suit. In fact, with the void in clubs, one could make a case that Roberta should bid 3D. However 2D is sufficient.|
