NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Let us count Roberta's Starting Points. 16 HCP, + two length points + two quality suits = 20. However, she knows they don't have a good spade fit, or if they do Dee has a really bad hand therefore, a spade game is fairly unlikely. 5D has plays, however, as it turns out.|
