NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now, I do have a quarrel with Patti's 3C bid. She does have a good suit but, it is only 5 cards and she has little else other than the King of hearts. Also, she knows Roberta is short in clubs, and I did not raise. Therefore, it is likely that Dee has some length in clubs. On the other hand, once she bids 3C, Dee must make a bid. She should either double or bid 3D.|
