NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|I would double. With a void in Roberta's first suit, it is likely the hand will go for a big number. The only thing a bit worrisome is Dee's four diamonds. Trump length is always good on defense  and the good thing about the diamond length is you can force Patti to ruff, and run her out of trumps. So, my first choice is double, my second choice is 3D. If you double, then you do better than bidding and making 5D. By not doubling, you ended up not doing as well as those people who bid game in diamonds.|
